<paragraph blockId="48.[189,1399,964,1026]" pageId="48" pageNumber="49">
The species name combines ʻ 
<emphasis box="[541,585,965,990]" italics="true" pageId="48" pageNumber="49">pict</emphasis>
ʼ (ʻpaintʼ) with ʻ 
<emphasis box="[781,858,965,990]" italics="true" pageId="48" pageNumber="49">pennis</emphasis>
ʼ (ʻwingʼ) and refers to the large reddish spot on the forewing.
</paragraph>
